<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:83215">
			
	<ab>		
		<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi>
	</ab>
	
	<p>
		tri-bhuvaṉa-cakkara-va<reg>r</reg>tti kōn-ēriṉmai-koṇṭāṉ Uṭaiyār tiru-k-koṭuṅ-kuṉṟam-uṭaiya nāyaṉār-kōyil tāṉattāṟku taṅkaḷūr viyā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character" precision="low"/> paṭai
		<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṅ kūṟṟuṭaṉ teru-p-poṅkaṟ kīḻ-p-poṟṟaikkum mīyāṟṟu-maṅkalattukkum maṭṭiyūr mēlai-k kuḷattukku mēṟkum
		vaḻicilai y-āṟṟukku vaṭakkum
		pe(ruṅ)
		<lb n="3"/>(kuṭi)kku kiḻakkum
		
		pūṇṭi-k-kuḷattukkum teṟkum
		Uṭpaṭṭa paṟṟil vaḻi Āyam Uḷḷatu mu-p-pattu mūṉṟ-āvatu mārkaḻi-mātam mutal Uṭaiyār tiru-k-koṭuṅ-kuṉṟa(m-u)
		<lb n="4"/>ṭaiya nāyaṉāṟkum nalla-maṅkaikkum puḻuku cāttukaikku Uṭalāka kuṭuttōm
	</p>
	<p>
		Ip-paṭikku Ivv-ōlai piṭi-pāṭāka-k koṇṭu cantirātitta-varai cella ka(l)
		<lb n="5" break="no"/>lilum cempilum veṭṭi-(k kuṭu)kka Ivv-ā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character" precision="low"/> taṅkaḷ Āḷiṭṭu Eṭuppittu puḻuku cāttuvittu-p pōtuka
	</p>
	<p>
		Ivai kula(cē)kara-p-pallavarāyaṉ Eḻuttu
	</p>
	<p>
		yāṇṭu <num value="33">3 <g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num> nā(ḷ)
	</p>
	<p>
		<lb n="6"/>Ivai (kā)li(ṅ)ka-rāyaṉ E(ḻu)ttu 		
 	</p>
</div>
	
